line poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3498270/extras/1415ee2f4224c2855a5bfda8b4584f41.poster.avif?t=1774524716\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3498270/extras/1415ee2f4224c2855a5bfda8b4584f41.webm?t=1774524716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3498270/extras/1415ee2f4224c2855a5bfda8b4584f41.mp4?t=1774524716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arrange the shelves, decorate, furnish, and create a unique place where customers will love to shop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹 Manages procurement and inventory</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3498270/extras/f2524f4fdd2471525c7b8c8eae7c42f9.poster.avif?t=1774524716\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3498270/extras/f2524f4fdd2471525c7b8c8eae7c42f9.webm?t=1774524716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3498270/extras/f2524f4fdd2471525c7b8c8eae7c42f9.mp4?t=1774524716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Monitor inventory levels, anticipate shortages, order products, and adjust your prices according to market trends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹 Keep your store spotless</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3498270/extras/06b68e097a0fb56068099400a02193d2.poster.avif?t=1774524716\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3498270/extras/06b68e097a0fb56068099400a02193d2.webm?t=1774524716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3498270/extras/06b68e097a0fb56068099400a02193d2.mp4?t=1774524716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clean the aisles, repair your machines, and monitor overall satisfaction to maintain your reputation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹 Receive your deliveries by truck</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3498270/extras/aa87f844b3cb98c0b2977b9a620ec0d1.poster.avif?t=1774524716\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3498270/extras/aa87f844b3cb98c0b2977b9a620ec0d1.webm?t=1774524716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3498270/extras/aa87f844b3cb98c0b2977b9a620ec0d1.mp4?t=1774524716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unload pallets, operate the pallet truck and stacker to fill your stockrooms and restock your shelves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹 Grow your business</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3498270/extras/bac9605ecfeaf7b79cd9aa2651a057ae.poster.avif?t=1774524716\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3498270/extras/bac9605ecfeaf7b79cd9aa2651a057ae.webm?t=1774524716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3498270/extras/bac9605ecfeaf7b79cd9aa2651a057ae.mp4?t=1774524716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hire, train, and supervise your employees. Improve their skills and invest in increasingly high-performance equipment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹 Multiplayer for up to 6 players</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3498270/extras/bf68241d2c773d88c0cdc63a7e88d440.poster.avif?t=1774524716\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3498270/extras/bf68241d2c773d88c0cdc63a7e88d440.webm?t=1774524716\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3498270/extras/bf68241d2c773d88c0cdc63a7e88d440.mp4?t=1774524716\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage your supermarket with others! Work together to optimize tasks, divide up roles, grow your business faster, or try to prove who is the best manager. A fun, chaotic, and unique cooperative experience in the world of management.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹 Provide an impeccable customer experience</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Analyze visitor behavior, optimize their journey, solve their problems, and avoid complaints that could damage your reputation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹 Unlock new specialty sectionsBakery, butcher shop, wine cellar, jewelry store, appliances, fruits and vegetables, fresh & frozen foods. Diversify your offerings and attract new customers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔹 Grow your empire Start small and become a leader with a thriving supermarket chain ready to dominate the market.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Ready to create the perfect supermarket?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Download the demo and discover management like you've never experienced it before.</p>",
